      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is a truly exceptional find! This vehicle is in flawless, mint condition and looks exactly like it did when it first left the showroom. Every inch has been meticulously preserved, from the gleaming exterior to the spotless interior, making it the perfect choice for a buyer who demands nothing but the absolute best.",
